title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP previews tonight's Chiefs/Chargers. DP commends Shannon Sharpe for his reaction to Brett Favre’s legal situation. Plus, Chris Simms of Pro Football Talk discusses the trade that would have sent Russell Wilson to the Browns.
